<div{{ attributes.addClass( data.class.office ) }}>
    <h2>{{ text.software_name }}</h2>
    {% include dir_office ~ '/templates/menu.html.twig' %}
    {% include dir_office ~ '/templates/message.html.twig' %}

    <div class="office-message">
        You have 3 tasks to do!<br>
        You have 2 urgent task to do!<br>
        You have 5 tasks to watch!<br>
    </div>
    <p>Getting Started Guide. After reading this guideline, you will be able to manage online office.</p>
    <div class="guide">
        <ol>
            <li>
                Terms
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Group - is a group or a company or a project.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Task - is a work to do. Tasks belong to a group.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li>
                Create a group
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        To start your group click on <a href="/office/group/add">create</a> under ALL GROUP menu.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b>Note: </b> If you are not admin, you may not create a group.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li>
                Create categories of task.
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Click the group and click category menu.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Input category like "Cars", "Clothes", "Shoes".
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li>
                Create a task
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Click group and click "create a task" button

                    <li>
                        Select category and fill other things
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Click Submit
                    </li>

                </ul>
            </li>

            <li>
                Track your task
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Track your task
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li>
                Advisory :
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        It is okay not to register as a member but recommanded.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>
